<h2>Viewing Moments</h2>
<p>View moment records organized by year in the person's detail screen.</p>
<ul>
  <li>Given and received items are displayed separately.</li>
  <li>Records with attached photos are shown with their images.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Editing/Deleting Moments</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Tap a recorded moment to edit its title, memo, photo, icon, etc.</li>
  <li>Records that are no longer needed can be deleted.</li>
</ul>
